title: Paul McCartney: Got Back
overview: FLOW's broadcast of Paul McCartney's return to Argentina with his famous "Got Back" tour, 5 years after his last visit to the country. Paul performed at the River Plate Stadium in the city of Buenos Aires on the 5th of October 2024. The performance featured the debut of 'Hi, Hi, Hi' on the tour's setlist, and the second ever live performance of the Beatle's final song 'Now & Then'.
